title: Swing Low, Sweet Chariot
lyrics: Comin' fo' to carry me home;
Comin' fo' to carry me home.
Comin' fo' to carry me home,
A band of angels comin' after me,
Comin' fo' to carry me home.
If you get there before I do,
Comin' fo' to carry me home,
Comin' fo' to carry me home.
Comin' fo' to carry me home,
When Jesus washed my sins away.
Comin' fo' to carry me home.
Comin' fo' to carry me home,
Comin' fo' to carry me home.
